import "./App.css";

import {
  Grid,
  Box,
  Typography,
  Button,
  CardMedia,
  CardContent,
  CardActions,
  Card,
} from "@mui/material";

import * as React from "react";

const mockEvents = [
  { name: "event1" },
  { name: "event2" },
  { name: "event3" },
  { name: "event4" },
  { name: "event5" },
];

function Events() {
  return (
    <Box padding={4}>
      <Box padding={2}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Events this week</Typography>
      </Box>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        {mockEvents.map((mockEvent) => (
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <Item>
              <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                <CardMedia
                  sx={{ height: 140 }}
                  image="/static/images/cards/contemplative-reptile.jpg"
                  title="green iguana"
                />
                <CardContent>
                  <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                    Lizard
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    Lizard events
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions>
                  <Button size="small">Share</Button>
                  <Button size="small">Learn More</Button>
                </CardActions>
              </Card>
            </Item>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Events;
